description: Wasteland is proud to present “Into The Mist” a BDSM themed soap opera with a supernatural twist. In the second episode of this series, Chloe learns that it is not only Willy that is subject to Mistress Victoria’s discipline. but she soon discovers her own dominant side when she finds Willy spying on her and Melissa in the garden. Both girls then finally meet the Master of the house, Grayson Rutherford (Dale Debone) and learn, to their horror that Rutherford Manor has “The Punishment Room”. (Episode 2 of 9)
title: Into the Mist - Episode 2: Into the Punishment Room
